;s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/osi-affiliate/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 22 Jun 2017 08:08:42 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/osi-affiliate/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:102:\"OSI Affiliate plugin allows customers to add affiliate tracking code to a WordPress website. It&#8230;\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"osiaffiliate\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2175:\"<p><!--section=description--></p>\n<p>OSI Affiliate plugin allows customers to add affiliate tracking code to a WordPress website. It makes it easy for you to create a referral marketing program for your WordPress. To use it, grab your affiliate tracking code from our platform. Next, go to our plugin and click add. Give it a name and then embed your tracking code. Our plugin will then generate a short code like: [short-code]<br />\nEach short code is unique. You can now take that short code and add it to a page in your WordPress. Now you can track referral sales that come through your WordPress.</p>\n<h4>Usage</h4>\n<p>To use the plugin, you are going to have to first get the affiliate tracking code from our platform. Then you are going to add this code into the plugin. Once you add the code into the plugin, our plugin will give you what we call snipplet short code which is code that you can place inside any page and when you place it inside a page, it will start tracking referrals.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Click to go into the plugin and click Add New HTML Snippet</li>\n<li>Enter a name and then enter the tracking code that you received.</li>\n<li>Next, you would see a confirmation message that the html snippet is added successfully.</li>\n<li>Select the Short code and copy it.</li>\n<li>Open a page from the wp admin panel pages option. This is the page where you want to add the tracking code. Open it and inside this page you are going to add the Snipplet Short Code.</li>\n<li>Paste the copied code into the Content Area of the page.</li>\n<li>Save/Update the Page and open/refresh it in the front end.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><!--section=installation--></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Download the WordPress plugin</li>\n<li>Upload the contents of the zip to your plugin directory</li>\n<li>Enable the plugin in your WordPress admin</li>\n</ol>\n<p><!--section=changelog--></p>\n<h4>1.1.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Launched the base version of the plugin</li>\n</ul>\n<p><!--section=faq--></p>\n<dl>\n<dt>Installation Instructions</dt>\n<dd>\n<ol>\n<li>Download the WordPress plugin</li>\n<li>Upload the contents of the zip to your plugin directory</li>\n<li>Enable the plugin in your WordPress admin</li>\n</ol>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35:\"Patreon Connect: Patron Memberships\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/patron-memberships-patreon-connect/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 22 Jun 2017 08:01:12 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/patreon-connect-patron-memberships/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"Use Patreon Connect with Paid Memberships Pro to give Patrons a membership level\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"uiux\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:969:\"<p><!--section=description--></p>\n<p>Harness the power of Patreon Connect in combination with other membership plugins such as Paid Memberships Pro. A Patrons contribution level will be matched with a corresponding membership level allowing you to utilise the potential of your Patreon campaign with the full suite of functionality offered with a large memberships plugin.</p>\n<p>Patrons will be treated as having the same membership level with the equivalent contrbution amounts.</p>\n<p>Currently only Paid Memberships Pro is featured, but if you would like to see any other memberships plugins support please get in touch with me @ <a href=\"https://uiux.me\" title=\"Patreon Connect\" rel=\"nofollow\">my website</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://uiux.me\" title=\"Patreon Connect\" rel=\"nofollow\">Patreon Connect</a> allows users to login to your websites with Patreon. You can restrict access to content by setting a default contribution level. You control who can see what.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"Image Hover Effects ultimate For Visual Composer\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/image-hover-effects-ultimate-visual-composer/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 22 Jun 2017 07:53:40 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/image-hover-effects-ultimate-visual-composer/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:94:\"Image Hover Effects Ultimate For Visual Composer allow User to add 62+ hover effects to&#8230;\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"biplob018\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lan